#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:74
msgid ""
"A default preparation display named :guilabel:`Kitchen Display` is "
"automatically configured when creating a new :doc:`restaurant point of sale "
"<../restaurant>` :ref:`through the onboarding screen <pos/use/create-pos>` "
"and selecting the :guilabel:`Restaurant` card."
msgstr ""
"يتم تكوين شاشة تحضير افتراضية باسم :guilabel:`Kitchen Display` تلقائيًا عند "
