msgstr "**قائمة رمز الاستجابة السريعة + الطلب**:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:105
msgid ""
"**Restaurants**: Customers can be served at their table or the pickup zone."
msgstr "**المطاعم**: يمكن خدمة العملاء على طاولتهم أو في منطقة الاستلام."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:107
msgid "When served at their table, they can pay after each meal or each order."
msgstr "عند خدمتهم على طاولتهم، يمكنهم الدفع بعد كل وجبة أو بعد كل طلب."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:108
msgid "When served at the pickup zone, they can only pay after each order."
msgstr "عند خدمتهم في منطقة الاستلام، يمكنهم الدفع فقط بعد كل طلب."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:109
msgid ""
"**Shops**: Customers can only be served at the pickup zone and pay after "
"each order."
msgstr ""
"**المتاجر**: يمكن خدمة العملاء فقط في منطقة الاستلام والدفع بعد كل طلب."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:110
msgid ""
"Regardless of the type of POS, customers can pay :doc:`online </applications/"
"finance/payment_providers>` or using any configured :doc:`payment method <../"
