msgstr "Pine Labs"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/pine_labs.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Pine Labs <https://www.pinelabs.com/instore-pos-machine>`_ offers in-store "
"payment solutions for customer transactions through several `physical "
"terminals <https://www.pinelabs.com/contact-sales?"
"tab=new&form=instorepayments>`_."
msgstr ""
"تقدم `Pine Labs <https://www.pinelabs.com/instore-pos-machine>`_ حلول الدفع "
"داخل المتجر لمعاملات العملاء من خلال عدة `أجهزة فعلية <https://"
"www.pinelabs.com/contact-sales?tab=new&form=instorepayments>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/pine_labs.rst:10
msgid "The Odoo Pine Labs module is only available for Indian companies."
msgstr "وحدة Odoo Pine Labs متاحة فقط للشركات الهندية."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/pine_labs.rst:11
msgid ""
"Pine Labs terminals accept credit/debit cards (Visa, MasterCard, and RuPay) "
"and UPI QR codes by swiping, scanning, or tapping."
msgstr ""
"تقبل أجهزة Pine Labs بطاقات الائتمان/الخصم (Visa وMasterCard وRuPay) ورموز "
"UPI QR عن طريق التمرير أو المسح أو النقر."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/pine_labs.rst:13
msgid ""
"When an Odoo database is hosted outside India, Pine Labs requires a proxy to "
"operate, as its services only accept traffic from Indian IP addresses. A "
"proxy ensures the connection is routed through India for better integration. "
"To activate a proxy on an Odoo Online or Odoo.sh database, `reach out to "
"Odoo support <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_."
msgstr ""
"عندما تستضاف قاعدة بيانات Odoo خارج الهند، تتطلب Pine Labs وكيلاً للعمل، حيث "
"أن خدماتها تقبل فقط حركة المرور من عناوين IP الهندية. يضمن الوكيل توجيه "
"الاتصال عبر الهند لتحسين التكامل. لتفعيل وكيل على قاعدة بيانات Odoo Online "
"أو Odoo.sh، `تواصل مع دعم Odoo <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/pine_labs.rst:21
