"the :guilabel:`QFPay` terminal, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"انتقل إلى :menuselection:`نقطة البيع --> الإعداد --> الإعدادات`، مرر لأسفل "
"إلى قسم :guilabel:`محطات الدفع الطرفية`، فعّل محطة :guilabel:`QFPay` الطرفية، "
"ثم انقر على :guilabel:`حفظ`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:61
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Integrate with` field to :guilabel:`QFPay`."
msgstr "اضبط حقل :guilabel:`Integrate with` على :guilabel:`QFPay`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:62
msgid ""
"Paste the copied information from :ref:`QFPay <pos/qfpay/configuration>` "
