#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/reporting.rst:36
msgid "The :guilabel:`Receipt Number`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`رقم الإيصال`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/reporting.rst:37
msgid "The :guilabel:`Customer`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`العميل`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/reporting.rst:38
msgid "The :guilabel:`Employee` that placed this order."
msgstr ":guilabel:`الموظف` الذي قدم هذا الطلب."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/reporting.rst:39
msgid "The :guilabel:`Total` paid amount."
msgstr "المبلغ :guilabel:`الإجمالي` المدفوع."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/reporting.rst:40
msgid "The order :guilabel:`Status`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`حالة` الطلب."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/reporting.rst:42
msgid ""
"To get an overview of all orders for a specific POS, regardless of the "
"session, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) "
"button on the POS card and select :guilabel:`Orders` from "
"the :guilabel:`View` section."
msgstr ""
"للحصول على نظرة عامة على جميع الطلبات لنقطة بيع محددة، بغض النظر عن الجلسة، "
"انقر على زر :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`القائمة العمودية`) على بطاقة "
"نقطة البيع واختر :guilabel:`الطلبات` من قسم :guilabel:`عرض`."

