msgstr "في شاشة الدفع، قم بتعيين عميل وحدد :guilabel:`الشحن لاحقًا`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:82
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, set a shipping date and click :guilabel:`Confirm` to "
